    "description": {
      "en": {
        "provenance": "imported",
        "value": "The Sikta Irrigation Project lies in Banke District in the Terai of the Mid-Western Development Region of Nepal, some 500 km west of Kathmandu generally as shown in Drawing Nr SIP/HW/ICB/01. The works mainly comprise the construction of Headworks for the irrigation of 34,000 ha of land in Banke District. The headworks will be constructed at Agaiya, nearly 20 km west from Kohalpur and located adjacent to the East West Highway."
      },
